Oh, i geeetttt ittt.

Repost:

JetV looked back to Artemis.  "I guess we figh....." he never 
finished the sentence as 17 shots rang into JetV's ATV mode, 
tipping him over.  Transforming JetV grabbed at holes in his fuel 
line.  

"Pa-a-cifix....we..w...we have...a ....situ...situation" he stuttered out 
through alot of pain.
